                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18400302-836-offence-1 t18400302-cd-46"></join>8th of February</rs>, 1 half-crown, and 1 shilling, the monies of <persName id="t18400302-name-307" type="victimName">
